irds', 50867, 0), (304218, 'Staying aloof from what''s keeping you away from Him is not works.', 19288, 0), (304219, 'Apologetics is reason flying to the rescue of faith', 3682, 0), (304220, 'Even gods are following trends. They are afraid to be forgotten by their creators', 3682, 0), (304221, 'One who trusts God at all costs will be rewarded at all costs.', 5104, 0), (304222, 'God doesn''t respond to your tears and emotions, He responds to your faith!', 18603, 0), (304223, 'Climbing mountains is strength', 50868, 0), (304224, 'Science does not need religion. Religion does not need science. And the twain shall never meet', 3682, 0), (304225, 'I love theologians, they know god cannot speak so they spend their energy trying to explain to us what his silence means', 3682, 0), (304226, 'God is good only when everything is good. When everything is bad, the devil takes control; god reappears when everything is in order once again. That''s what my pastor taught me.', 3682, 0), (304227, 'Religion teaches us to fight against our natural instincts but it thrives on them', 3682, 0), (304228, 'Well, I suppose if I did exactly what I wanted to do with perfection for a long time in my life, the same way, it would have been very boring. There is always a spirit that sees around the next corner, knows the heart of the person you next meet, and might want you to try something you never did before, we call this faith and it makes life all the more worth while living.', 5405, 0), (304229, 'Plowing through life, you’re bound to run into obstructions. Some of life’s trials result from mistakes and missteps, and some from poor choices. I know about that too, because I’ve made my share of blunders and had to face the consequences.Other times, the unexpected lands in your hands like a wayward ball and the “trouble” coming at you is like a 250-pound linebacker blitzing straight off the edge.￼', 37877, 0), (304230, 'When the football is handed to the ball carrier, everyone counts on that guy