ie and move in and out of our lives. The dreams and goals of today will one day either materialize or evolve into something different with time. If we become rigidly attached to any of this, we set ourselves up for the inevitable suffering that will ensue when the thing, person or idea flows out of our lives, or our desire for it shifts.', 29774, 0), (304393, 'It is key to remember we can maintain a genuine enthusiasm and love for what IS, in the PRESENT moment, enjoy it with gratitude for all of the blessings in our lives.', 29774, 0), (304394, 'Whether you’re at the peak or the valley of any given wave, remember that this too shall pass.', 29774, 0), (304395, 'When we return continually to the present moment and our centered awareness within it, we remember we are eternally connected to the Supreme Source that lives within us.', 29774, 0), (304396, 'We will attract potential partners who reflect back to us what we need to heal, balance and strengthen in ourselves- until we become whole. At that point, we can attract our twin flame or soul mate and enjoy a peaceful co- creative partnership that benefits all of mankind.', 29774, 0), (304397, 'When we are open, strong and fluid in our body, we are experiencing the best that life has to offer with very little limitation or constraints.', 29774, 0), (304398, 'We always want to share and cherish our moments from Happiness.', 12522, 0), (304399, 'When you release a trauma on one level of your energetic being, you will experience relief on all other levels simultaneously.', 29774, 0), (304400, 'Happiness is euphoria of the mind', 45951, 0);
